      "title": "A 5 2 n 2 -lower bound for the rank of n \u00d7 n-matrix multiplication over arbitrary fields",
      "abstract": "We prove a lower bound of 5/2n/sup 2/-3n for the rank of n/spl times/n-matrix multiplication over an arbitrary field. Similar bounds hold for the rank of the multiplication in noncommutative division algebras and for the multiplication of upper triangular matrices."
    }
